	   <tr><td colspan=2>Path to Velious armor:<br>Reinforced to 108. Start Wu's Belts (triv 128) work through Wu's Tunic (triv 158). The Wu's is pretty easy to make and will sell pretty good in EC. At this point you can either try your luck at Velious stuff, or make Fleeting Quivers (which will triv around 220). Always try to find a buyer for a quiver before you attempt it a few times, as the gems get a bit expensive. Definatly get your wis or int as high as possible, to max skill ups and successes.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>~ Zonkz ~<br></td></tr>
