	   <tr><td colspan=2>Othmir Fur armor is made from the fur of various Othmirs in Cobalt Scar.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Othmir warriors and shaman are around 40-45.  There are othmir pups, but I'm not positive they drop the needed furs.  For the cloak you'll need the following:<br><br>4 Othmir Furs [Velious]<br>1 Silver Thread [Velious]<br>1 Cloak Pattern<br>1 vial of Clear Mana [Velious]<br><br>You can purchase the thread at the vendors in Thurgadin.  The clear mana is made with a 29th level enchanter spell that requires a poison vial, and 1 emerald.  Combine the components in a large sewing kit, and do not stack the furs.  Good luck, you tailors!  Hope this has helped:)  Be safe, and leave some time for RL.<br><br>PS  Othmirs also drop Custacean Shell Armor:)<br>&nbsp;<br>Hyden Endabrush<br>Expert Scout of the Fay</td></tr>
